SAST tool


Penetration Testing:

Process of hacking
- Information Gathering
- Threat Modeling
- Vulnerability Analysis
- Exploitation 
- Post-Exploitation
- Reporting

5 phases
- Information Gathering
- Scanning
- Gaining Access
- Maintaining Access
- Clearing Tracks


Static Testing - Testing without deploying the code.
Dynamic Testing - Testing with deploying the code.

